      • sqrt

        BigComplex sqrt(MathContext mc)
        The square root.
        Returns:
        the square root of the this. The branch is chosen such that the imaginary part of the result has the same sign as the imaginary part of this.
        Since:
        2008-10-27
        See Also:
        Ahrendt, Fast High-precision computation of complex square roots, ISSAC 1996 p142-149.
